TopicTitle: Please help me. I don't have the gigantic parts of B9 Aerospace

Articles.Content:

I put everything in the Game data folder but When I start everything up, i do not have them.

Please help me in the name of Jeb.
It was split into a separate download. The large "HX" parts are available here on Kerbal Stuff.
